title: Wafflehouse Competition Winner
body:
Due to the voting mechanism of the wafflehouse.io app being manipulated and the system was flooded with uncreative entries just to be able to vote, YFL core team has decided to give the power back to the community and let the YFL governance vault stakers decide who the winners of the Wafflehouse competition are. Therefore we're using the Snapshot voting mechanic to redo the voting!

These are the eligible entries, sorted according to creation date: https://logos.linkswap.app/wafflehouse-entries.png

#1: 0xe59A79C7516d22A488A3F479626E75a2e81aAE66
#2:0x2fd0476478C01D0472b264e27F9D3C1b30DAda2A

#9: 0xa924d8A934299329A44a7b6911c0d7ED6Cfa6ff1
#10: 0xf68C60DE6ccba955BD2Ed921430472032dF61BAe

The winner receives the grand prize of $5000 in $ONE tokens as stated in the blog post: https://blog.yflink.io/harmony-and-linkswap-release-blockchain-game-waffle-house/

We will be returning the rest of the funds to the Harmony team, as they had provided the tokens for the grand prize.
choices: #4 lone wolf waffle made of choc
